#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "Referenca ukazov"

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:6
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter gives detailed explanations of all commands available in "
"&partman;. It is intended as a reference to accompany the information given "
"in <xref linkend=\"usermanual\"/>."
msgstr ""
"V tem poglavju so podrobne razlage vseh ukazov, ki so na voljo v &partman;. "
"Namenjen je kot referenca, ki spremlja informacije v <xref linkend="
"\"usermanual\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:14
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Quit</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Quits &partman;</action> without applying any pending operations. "
"The application will however ask you to confirm your choice to quit if there "
"are pending operations."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zapre &partman;</action> brez uporabe čakajočih operacij. Vendar pa "
"vas bo aplikacija pozvala, da potrdite svojo izbiro za izstop, če obstajajo "
"čakajoče operacije."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "Meni Urejanje"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Undo</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Z</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razveljavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Undoes the last operation</action> that has been added to the "
"operation stack."
msgstr ""
"<action>Razveljavi zadnjo operacijo</action>, ki je bila dodana v sklad "
"operacij."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:46 referencemanual.docbook:62
#: referencemanual.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command is only enabled if the list of operations is not empty."
msgstr "Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če seznam operacij ni prazen."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Clear</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Počisti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Clears the list of operations</action> without applying any of them."
msgstr ""
"<action>Počisti seznam operacij</action>, ne da bi uporabil katero koli od "
"njih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Apply</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uporabi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Applies the list of operations</action>. This command will apply all "
"operations in the list so that all changes are permanently written to your "
"disks. After the operations have been applied, the list is cleared and there "
"will be no way to undo any operation."
msgstr ""
"<action>Uporabi seznam operacij</action>. Ta ukaz bo uporabil vse operacije "
"na seznamu, tako da bodo vse spremembe trajno zapisane na vaše diske. Ko so "
"operacije uporabljene, se seznam počisti in nobene operacije ne bo mogoče "
"razveljaviti."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Device Menu"
msgstr "Meni naprave"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Select Current Device</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izberi trenutno napravo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to select a device from a submenu with all available devices of "
"the system."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča izbiro naprave iz podmenija z vsemi razpoložljivimi napravami "
"sistema."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Device</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Refresh Devices</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F5</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Osveži naprave</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Refreshes the devices</action>: This command forces &partman; to "
"scan and read the devices on your computer again. This may for example be "
"useful if you plugged in an external USB hard disk after you started "
"&partman;."
msgstr ""
"<action>Osveži naprave</action>: Ta ukaz prisili &partman; za ponovno "
"skeniranje in branje naprav v vašem računalniku. To je lahko na primer "
"uporabno, če ste po zagonu &partman; priključili zunanji trdi disk USB."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Partition "
"Table</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova "
"particijska tabela</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Creates a new partition table</action>: This command creates a new "
"and empty GPT or MSDOS partition table on the currently selected device. "
"This will delete all partitions on the device and all data on them, so you "
"will want to be careful with this command."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ustvari novo particijsko tabelo</action>: Ta ukaz ustvari novo in "
"prazno particijsko tabelo GPT ali MSDOS na trenutno izbrani napravi. S tem "
"boste izbrisali vse particije v napravi in vse podatke na njih, zato bodite "
"pri tem ukazu previdni."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a device is selected and no partition on "
"this device is currently mounted."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrana naprava in na tej napravi trenutno ni "
"nameščena nobena particija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export Partition Table</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvoz particijske tabele</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Allows you to export a list of all partitions on the selected device into a "
"file."
msgstr "Omogoča izvoz seznama vseh particij na izbrani napravi v datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Partition Table</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvoz particijske tabele</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allows you to import partition table from a previously exported file."
msgstr "Omogoča uvoz particijske tabele iz predhodno izvožene datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will delete all partitions on the device and all data on them, so you "
"will want to be careful with this command."
msgstr ""
"S tem boste izbrisali vse particije v napravi in vse podatke na njih, zato "
"bodite pri tem ukazu previdni."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a device is selected and no partition on "
"this device is currently mounted. Importing into logical devices such as LVM "
"Volume Groups is currently not supported."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrana naprava in na tej napravi trenutno ni "
"nameščena nobena particija. Uvoz v logične naprave, kot so skupine nosilcev "
"LVM, trenutno ni podprt."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>SMART Status</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> <guimenuitem>STATUS SMART</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a SMART report. SMART is a monitoring system included in hard disk and "
"solid-state drives that detects and reports on various indicators of drive "
"reliability, with the intent of enabling the anticipation of hardware "
"failures."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže poročilo SMART. SMART je nadzorni sistem, ki je vključen v trde "
"diske in pogone SSD, ki zaznava in poroča o različnih indikatorjih "
"zanesljivosti pogona, z namenom omogočiti predvidevanje okvar strojne opreme."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Device</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Naprava</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows information about currently selected devices. In this dialog you can "
"find capacity, sector sizes, partition table type as well as used and "
"maximum number of primary partitions."
msgstr ""
"Prikazuje informacije o trenutno izbranih napravah. V tem pogovornem oknu "
"lahko najdete zmogljivost, velikosti sektorjev, vrsto particijske tabele ter "
"uporabljeno in največje število primarnih particij."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Partition Menu"
msgstr "Meni particije"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Novo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Creates a new partition</action>: Opens the dialog to create a new "
"partition where you will be able to set type, size, position and file system "
"of the partition to create."
msgstr ""
"<action>Ustvari novo particijo</action>: Odpre pogovorno okno za ustvarjanje "
"nove particije, kjer boste lahko nastavili vrsto, velikost, položaj in "
"datotečni sistem particije, ki jo želite ustvariti."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please note that the partition table on a device may impose restrictions on "
"how many partitions can be created. MS-DOS partition tables, for example, "
"allow only four primary partitions."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da lahko tabela particij v napravi naloži omejitve glede "
"števila particij, ki jih je mogoče ustvariti. Particijske tabele MS-DOS na "
"primer dovoljujejo samo štiri primarne particije."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if an unallocated area on a device is selected."
msgstr "Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrano nedodeljeno območje v napravi."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Resize/Move</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spremeni velikost/"
"premakni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Resizes or moves a partition</action>: Opens the dialog to resize or "
"move an existing partition. Depending on the partition's file system and the "
"external tools installed on your computer, not all three possible resize-"
"related actions -- that is, moving the partition, making it smaller "
"(<quote>shrinking</quote> it) or making it larger (<quote>growing</quote> "
"it) -- may be available in this dialog. See <xref linkend=\"menu-tools-"
"filesystemsupport\"/>."
msgstr ""
"<action>Spremeni velikost ali premakne particijo</action>: Odpre pogovorno "
"okno za spreminjanje velikosti ali premikanje obstoječe particije. Odvisno "
"od datotečnega sistema particije in zunanjih orodij, nameščenih v vašem "
"računalniku, niso vsa tri možna dejanja, povezana s spreminjanjem velikosti "
"-- to je premikanje particije, njeno pomanjševanje (<quote>krčenje</quote>) "
"ali povečanje (<quote>goje</quote>) -- morda je na voljo v tem pogovornem "
"oknu. Glejte <xref linkend=\"menu-tools-filesystemsupport\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected that is not "
"currently mounted and whose file system can be shrunk, grown or moved. For "
"an extended partition, it is only enabled if none of the logicals in the "
"extended partition are mounted."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen samo, če je izbrana particija, ki trenutno ni nameščena "
"in katere datotečni sistem je mogoče skrčiti, povečati ali premakniti. Za "
"razširjeno particijo je omogočeno le, če nobena od logičnih elementov v "
"razširjeni particiji ni nameščena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut>&Del;</shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Delete</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut>&Del;</shortcut> <guimenu>Particija</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izbriši</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Deletes a partition</action>: This command deletes the currently "
"selected partition."
msgstr ""
"<action>Izbriše particijo</action>: Ta ukaz izbriše trenutno izbrano "
"particijo."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:245 referencemanual.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected that is not "
"currently mounted. For an extended partition, it is only enabled if it does "
"not contain any logical partitions."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrana particija, ki trenutno ni nameščena. "
"Za razširjeno particijo je omogočeno le, če ne vsebuje logičnih particij."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:249 referencemanual.docbook:311
#: referencemanual.docbook:398 referencemanual.docbook:431
#: referencemanual.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "Warning: Possible loss of data"
msgstr "Opozorilo: možna izguba podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:250
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting a partition means that all data on the partition is destroyed."
msgstr "Brisanje particije pomeni, da so vsi podatki na particiji uničeni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Del;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Shred</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Del;</keycombo></shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Razdrobi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shreds a partition</action>: This command shreds the currently "
"selected partition."
msgstr ""
"<action>Uniči particijo</action>: Ta ukaz uniči trenutno izbrano particijo."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Warning: Loss of data"
msgstr "Opozorilo: Izguba podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shredding a partition means that all data on the partition is destroyed."
msgstr "Uničenje particije pomeni, da so vsi podatki na particiji uničeni."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Copies a partition</action>: This command copies the currently "
"selected partition to &partman;'s clipboard."
msgstr ""
"<action>Kopira particijo</action>: Ta ukaz kopira trenutno izbrano particijo "
"v &partman; odložišče."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected that is not "
"currently mounted and whose file system can be copied. Extended partitions "
"can not be copied."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrana particija, ki trenutno ni nameščena in "
"katere datotečni sistem je mogoče kopirati. Razširjenih particij ni mogoče "
"kopirati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Paste</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prilepi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Paste a partition</action>: This command pastes the partition from "
"&partman;'s clipboard to the currently selected partition or unallocated "
"area."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prilepi particijo</action>: Ta ukaz prilepi particijo iz &partman; "
"odložišča na trenutno izbrano particijo ali nedodeljeno območje."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:304
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When pasting to an unallocated area, a dialog will open allowing you to move "
"or grow the inserted copy. When overwriting an existing partition this "
"dialog will not be shown."
msgstr ""
"Pri lepljenju na nedodeljeno območje se odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem "
"lahko premaknete ali povečate vstavljeno kopijo. Pri prepisovanju obstoječe "
"particije to pogovorno okno ne bo prikazano."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is currently in the clipboard "
"and a valid target (either a partition or an unallocated area) is selected. "
"The target must also be large enough to hold the source and can not be "
"mounted. You can not copy a partition onto itself."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je particija trenutno v odložišču in je izbran "
"veljaven cilj (bodisi particija bodisi nedodeljeno območje). Tarča mora biti "
"tudi dovolj velika, da drži vir in je ni mogoče namestiti. Particije ne "
"morete kopirati nase."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pasting a partition on an existing one means that all data on the existing "
"partition is destroyed and replaced with the data from the pasted partition."
msgstr ""
"Lepljenje particije na obstoječo pomeni, da se vsi podatki na obstoječi "
"particiji uničijo in nadomestijo s podatki iz prilepljene particije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Edit Mount Point</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Urejanje točke priklopa</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Opens a dialog</action> to edit the mount point and the mount "
"options."
msgstr ""
"<action>Odpre pogovorno okno</action> za urejanje točke priklopa in možnosti "
"priklopa."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "This command is only enabled if a partition is unmounted."
msgstr "Ta ukaz je omogočen samo, če je particija odklopljena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Mount/Unmount</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pripni/odpni</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Mounts or unmounts a partition</action>: This command mounts or "
"unmounts the selected partition, depending on its current state."
msgstr ""
"<action>Priklopi ali odklopi particijo</action>: Ta ukaz priklopi ali "
"odklopi izbrano particijo, odvisno od njenega trenutnega stanja."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected that can be mounted "
"or unmounted. If the operating system does not know a mount point for the "
"partition you can not mount it from &partman;."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrana particija, ki jo je mogoče priklopiti "
"ali odklopiti. Če operacijski sistem ne pozna točke priklopa za particijo, "
"je ne morete pripeti iz &partman;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Check</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preveri</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Checks a partition</action>: This command checks the selected "
"partition and its file system for errors and tries to correct any problems "
"it finds. During this process the file system on the partition will also be "
"resized to fill the partition completely."
msgstr ""
"<action>Preveri particijo</action>: Ta ukaz preveri izbrano particijo in "
"njen datotečni sistem za napake in poskuša popraviti morebitne težave, ki "
"jih najde. Med tem postopkom bo spremenjena tudi velikost datotečnega "
"sistema na particiji, da bo popolnoma zapolnila particijo."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected that can be checked "
"and is not currently mounted."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrana particija, ki jo je mogoče preveriti "
"in trenutno ni nameščena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Backup</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Varnostna kopija</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:372
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Backs up a partition</action>: This command backs up the file system "
"on the selected partition to a file. You will be asked where to store the "
"image file after activating this command."
msgstr ""
"<action>Varnostno kopira particijo</action>: Ta ukaz varnostno kopira "
"datotečni sistem na izbrani particiji v datoteko. Po aktiviranju tega ukaza "
"boste pozvani, kam shraniti slikovno datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The created image file is a sector-for-sector copy of the file system on the "
"partition. It is not compressed and does not have any additional meta "
"information or header added to it, thus it can be directly mounted using a "
"loop device outside of &partman; if the operating system supports that."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjena slikovna datoteka je sektorska kopija datotečnega sistema na "
"particiji. Ni stisnjen in nima dodanih nobenih dodatnih meta informacij ali "
"glave, zato ga je mogoče neposredno namestiti z uporabo zanke zunaj "
"&partman; če operacijski sistem to podpira."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This command is only enabled if a partition is selected and the file system "
"on it can be backed up. The partition must also not be mounted."
msgstr ""
"Ta ukaz je omogočen le, če je particija izbrana in je datotečni sistem na "
"njej mogoče varnostno kopirati. Predelna stena tudi ne sme biti montirana."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:385
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Restore</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Obnovi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Restores a partition</action>: This command restores a file system "
"from an image file to a partition. You will be asked for the name of the "
"image file to restore after activating this command. The target to restore "
"to must be large enough for the image file."
msgstr ""
"<action>Obnovi particijo</action>: Ta ukaz obnovi datotečni sistem iz "
"slikovne datoteke na particijo. Po aktiviranju tega ukaza boste morali "
"vnesti ime slikovne datoteke, ki jo želite obnoviti. Cilj za obnovitev mora "
"biti dovolj velik za slikovno datoteko."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command is only enabled if either an unallocated area is selected or a "
"partition that is not currently mounted."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrano nedodeljeno območje ali particija, ki "
"trenutno ni nameščena."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Restoring a partition on an existing one means that all data on the existing "
"partition is destroyed and replaced with the data from the restored image "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Obnovitev particije na obstoječi particiji pomeni, da se vsi podatki na "
"obstoječi particiji uničijo in nadomestijo s podatki iz obnovljene slikovne "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Partition</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Particija</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shows a partition's properties</action>: This command shows a dialog "
"with information about the currently selected partition or unallocated space."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže lastnosti particije</action>: Ta ukaz prikaže pogovorno okno "
"z informacijami o trenutno izbrani particiji ali nedodeljenem prostoru."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What is displayed and what can be modified in this dialog depends on the "
"type of partition, the type of the file system on the partition and on the "
"partition being currently mounted or not."
msgstr ""
"Kaj je prikazano in kaj je mogoče spremeniti v tem pogovornem oknu, je "
"odvisno od vrste particije, vrste datotečnega sistema na particiji in od "
"particije, ki je trenutno nameščena ali ne."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:417
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all file systems, for example, support setting a label. It is also "
"generally not possible to modify any properties if the partition is mounted."
msgstr ""
"Vsi datotečni sistemi na primer ne podpirajo nastavitve oznake. Prav tako na "
"splošno ni mogoče spremeniti nobenih lastnosti, če je particija nameščena."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a list of all partition and file system properties that can in "
"general be modified in this dialog:"
msgstr ""
"To je seznam vseh particij in lastnosti datotečnega sistema, ki jih je na "
"splošno mogoče spremeniti v tem pogovornem oknu:"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set or modify a file system's label"
msgstr "Nastavite ali spremenite oznako datotečnega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the partition's file system."
msgstr "Spremenite datotečni sistem particije."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Changing the file system for a partition always means that all data on the "
"partition is destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Spreminjanje datotečnega sistema za particijo vedno pomeni, da so vsi "
"podatki na particiji uničeni."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recreate the file system on the partition"
msgstr "Ponovno ustvarite datotečni sistem na particiji"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Recreating a file system on a partition always means that all data on the "
"partition is destroyed. Recreating a file system should only be used as a "
"last resort if the file system on a partition cannot be repaired anymore."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno ustvarjanje datotečnega sistema na particiji vedno pomeni, da so vsi "
"podatki na particiji uničeni. Ponovno ustvarjanje datotečnega sistema je "
"treba uporabiti le kot zadnjo možnost, če datotečnega sistema na particiji "
"ni več mogoče popraviti."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change a partition's flags"
msgstr "Spremenite zastavice particije"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the type of partition table used, there will be several flags "
"available for each partition on the partition table. In most cases, "
"modifying the flags is not necessary and should be considered an advanced "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"Glede na vrsto uporabljene particijske tabele bo za vsako particijo na "
"particijski tabeli na voljo več zastavic. V večini primerov spreminjanje "
"zastavic ni potrebno in ga je treba obravnavati kot napredno funkcijo."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The command is only enabled if either an unallocated area or a partition is "
"selected."
msgstr "Ukaz je omogočen le, če je izbrano nedodeljeno območje ali particija."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tools Menu"
msgstr "Meni Orodja"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Volume Group</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>L</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nova skupina "
"nosilcev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new logical device such as <link linkend=\"glossary-lvm\">LVM</"
"link> Volume Group."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite novo logično napravo, kot je skupina nosilcev <link linkend="
"\"glossary-lvm\">LVM</link>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: referencemanual.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>File System Support</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Podpora za datotečni sistem</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Shows the file system support dialog.</action> This dialog shows in "
"detail which operations can be performed for which of the supported file "
"systems."
msgstr ""
"<action>Prikaže pogovorno okno za podporo datotečnega sistema.</action> To "
"pogovorno okno podrobno prikazuje, katere operacije je mogoče izvesti za "
"katerega od podprtih datotečnih sistemov."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is an example how the dialog might look like with most external tools "
"installed:"
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je primer, kako bi lahko izgledalo pogovorno okno z večino nameščenih "
"zunanjih orodij:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: referencemanual.docbook:493
#, no-c-format
msgid "File system support dialog with most external tools installed"
msgstr ""
"Pogovorno okno za podporo datotečnega sistema z večino nameščenih zunanjih "
"orodij"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The blue check marks mean <quote>supported</quote>, the red crosses mean "
"<quote>not supported</quote>. Some combinations are never supported, for "
"example checking a linuxswap file system, because they are inherently "
"impossible. Others cannot be supported because the external tools lack the "
"functionality."
msgstr ""
"Modre kljukice pomenijo <quote>podprto</quote>, rdeči križci pomenijo "
"<quote>ni podprto</quote>. Nekatere kombinacije niso nikoli podprte, na "
"primer preverjanje datotečnega sistema linuxswap, ker so same po sebi "
"nemogoče. Drugih ni mogoče podpreti, ker zunanjim orodjem primanjkuje "
"funkcionalnosti."

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed new tools while &partman; is running click on "
"<guibutton>Rescan Support</guibutton> to force a recheck of installed file "
"system support tools."
msgstr ""
"Če ste namestili nova orodja, medtem ko &partman; se izvaja, kliknite "
"<guibutton>Ponovno skeniraj podporo</guibutton>, da vsilite ponovno "
"preverjanje nameščenih orodij za podporo datotečnega sistema."

#. Tag: title
#: referencemanual.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: referencemanual.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&partman; has the common &kde; <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-settings\">Settings</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Help</ulink> menu described in the &kde; "
"Fundamentals with an additional submenu <guisubmenu>Panels Shown</"
"guisubmenu>, where you can toggle the display of the <guimenuitem>Devices</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Pending Operations</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Information</guimenuitem> and panels <guimenuitem>Log Output</"
"guimenuitem> on and off."
msgstr ""
"&partman; ima skupno &kde; Meni <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-settings\">Nastavitve</ulink> in <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/"
"menus.html#menus-help\">Pomoč</ulink> opisano v &kde; Osnove z dodatnim "
"podmenijem <guisubmenu>Prikazane plošče</guisubmenu>, kjer lahko "
"preklapljate med prikazom <guimenuitem>Naprave</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Operacije v teku</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Informacije</"
"guimenuitem> in plošče <guimenuitem>Izpis dnevnika</guimenuitem> vklop in "
"izklop."
